Package suncertify.client

Interface Summary
RoomReservationsModel A model for the list of hotel rooms returned by a search.
 

Class Summary
LookupRoomReservations Service locator class for looking up the room reservation system.
MainController The controller in the Model-View-Controller architecture of the room reservation system.
MainWindow The main client application window.
RoomReservationsDelegate Delegate class for clients of the URLyBird Room Reservation System.
URLyBirdModel Model implementation of the room reservation system's MVC design.
 

Exception Summary
RoomReservationsException Thrown when a client cannot connect to the room reservations system via the business delegate class RoomReservationsDelegate.
